data.description: Views, custom design, open concept, primary suite WITH  A CUPOLA...and those are just the highlights! 378 Cross Hill has ample space that is thoughtfully laid out. Ready to entertain with open concept living and kitchen with an added bonus of an eat in kitchen island for a more casual meal. Magnetic views right from the entertaining space complete with a dramatic staircase all of which flows right out on to your wrap around deck. Prefer a more formal eat in dining space? Or looking for an office? This home has it all. With space to expand in the walk out basement, a beautiful yard to play in and 5.55 acres to explore. Just 10 minutes to down town Augusta and 95, you get the 'country' feel with the added bonus of convenience. The private 3rd floor primary suite makes for a restful, private space. Three heat sources allowing you to feel as cozy and warm or as cool as you desire, depending on weather and your personal comfort level. Added storage with the oversized shed allowing room for your off season needs, a mower AND snowblower! This house feels home the second you walk in, come take a look and find out! Home has a two bedroom septic.
